text: The Deportivo CAFESSA, commonly known as CAFESSA, is a Mexican football club based in Guadalajara. The club was founded in 2015, and currently plays in the Liga TDP. Previously, the club maintained another Liga TDP team at Tonalá, Jalisco, in addition, another team that played in the Liga Premier – Serie B In June 2019, Deportivo CAFESSA Jalisco was created, before, CAFESSA Tlajomulco served as the main team of the franchise. Subsequently, after the creation of CAFESSA Jalisco, it became the main reserve team of the club, although maintaining its own identity with respect to Jalisco. ==Players== ===Current squad=== == See also == * Deportivo CAFESSA Jalisco == References == Category:Association football clubs established in 2015 Category:Football clubs in Jalisco Category:2015 establishments in Mexico Category:Liga Premier de México
